name: .QEWE File Extension
summary: Learn about .QEWE files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: Because QEWE files are encrypted, you cannot open them. At this time, there is no way to decrypt QEWE files. The best way to restore files encrypted by QEWE ransomware is to retrieve them from a recent backup or perform a System Restore.
